{"id": 995, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么时候你会觉得“啊可惜没人见证这一刻”？", "description": "天啊，你们错失了多少个风姿绰约、风流倜傥、光彩夺目、机智勇敢、完美无瑕的我！（题图来自：simone massoni）", "record_count": 4465, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607031301341vwGnMjiExpVyXau.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-15T01:00:58Z", "options": [{"id": 78593, "content": "扔垃圾的时候在很远的距离精准的扔进了垃圾桶里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606462}, {"id": 78338, "content": "好不容易助人为乐的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562369}, {"id": 81922, "content": "宿醉第二天醒来皮肤依然很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622537}, {"id": 78341, "content": "赚第一笔金的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608955}, {"id": 78342, "content": "有时候并不是“可惜没人见证”，而是“能跟你一起见证该有多好”", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370361}, {"id": 78599, "content": "五杀的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541342}, {"id": 78345, "content": "吃的了好吃的食物 看到了美妙的风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605790}, {"id": 80137, "content": "随手丢废纸擦边进了垃圾桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615707}, {"id": 78346, "content": "看到了熟悉的电影画面", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605790}, {"id": 78348, "content": "刚洗完澡把湿头发捋到后面在擦了水雾的镜子面前的我", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254444}, {"id": 78350, "content": "照镜子觉得自己特别漂亮的某一刻。哈哈……", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602273}, {"id": 78606, "content": "有一次早上起床时两个眼睛都变成了双眼皮（本人是单眼皮），特别自然，特别好看～", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609320}, {"id": 78352, "content": "哼了一个自创的demo，刚想录下来或者哼给别人听时，就彻底忘了???", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125968}, {"id": 78353, "content": "跑步跑了13公里、很厉害了吧 ? 但是完成这个壮举的时候、没有人陪在我身边。也许早已习惯孤身一人", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196274}, {"id": 79894, "content": "做了一盘好菜的时候，啊，可惜没有人陪我一起品尝。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613587}, {"id": 78359, "content": "做了一个很牛逼的事情以后", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608931}, {"id": 80152, "content": "减肥称上轻了的体重", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538207}, {"id": 78361, "content": "稳稳接住一个即将掉落的东西 想炫耀 发现四下无人 lol", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513660}, {"id": 78362, "content": "好像永远没有这种时刻，长这么大还没成功过呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595016}, {"id": 78363, "content": "看了牛逼的书或纪录片懂了很冷门的知识，结果他妈根本没机会和别人聊到", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609045}, {"id": 78109, "content": "吃泡泡糖 吹了一个超大的泡泡", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508569}, {"id": 78365, "content": "浑身湿漉漉从衣服里透出的?肌肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 537954}, {"id": 78110, "content": "一气呵成拉了一条很长很长颜色健康干湿适中的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 386, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468920}, {"id": 78111, "content": "发的这么厉害评论居然没人点赞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 276, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323059}, {"id": 78623, "content": "暂时没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609840}, {"id": 78112, "content": "做出了平常做不出来的炫酷动作", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608022}, {"id": 78113, "content": "刚锻炼完汗流浃背却活力满满的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 234, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608024}, {"id": 78369, "content": "每当照镜子的时候，发现只有自己一人的脸。无敌是多么寂寞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603990}, {"id": 78114, "content": " penta kill。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224897}, {"id": 78370, "content": "每当照镜子的时候，总会想起一句话:无敌是多么寂寞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603990}, {"id": 78116, "content": "单身汪做了一碗香的晕过去的销魂饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542160}, {"id": 78372, "content": "出了丑，很可爱的那种～", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592232}, {"id": 78117, "content": "我穿的特别美，却没有人愿意替我拍照/拜拜", "image": null, "praise_count": 197, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254456}, {"id": 78118, "content": "单身汪做了一碗香的晕过去的销魂饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 192, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542160}, {"id": 78119, "content": "penta q 的时候！打完这把必须截图发个朋友圈！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607613}, {"id": 78376, "content": "一个人踢足球练习射门进了个角度刁钻的任意球", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605426}, {"id": 78121, "content": "洗完澡后发现变帅的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599122}, {"id": 78377, "content": "周围人不看美剧，无法和他们交流各种笑点和梗", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600451}, {"id": 78123, "content": "独自亲眼见证照片拍不出的美景", "image": null, "praise_count": 704, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199459}, {"id": 78380, "content": "刚洗完头还没干的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521828}, {"id": 78125, "content": "人为什么有时候会难受?，伤心?，求解", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608044}, {"id": 78381, "content": "瞬间接起要落到地上的玻璃杯", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130933}, {"id": 78126, "content": "被一部纪录片深深影响打动，有一堆牛逼的人生思考，做出了移民的决定，却没有人和我探讨细节.....孤独吞噬了梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 276, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606680}, {"id": 78382, "content": "很久没玩的游戏突然间玩得特别顺特别厉害", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182959MzkSYRZD1cQfpHLx.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609147}, {"id": 78127, "content": "每次照镜子的时候~", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 11479}, {"id": 78384, "content": "独自写出数学/物理题", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 371344}, {"id": 79409, "content": "打游戏正嗨的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527480}, {"id": 78131, "content": "洗澡歌神", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606709}, {"id": 78387, "content": "风景很美的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540686}, {"id": 78132, "content": "突然吐出一个烟圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606709}]}